Reasoning: The paper discusses the influence of Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Artificial Life (ALife) technologies upon society, and their potential to fundamentally shape the future evolution of humankind. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI. The paper also explores the history of these concepts, which could fall under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.HCI (Human-Computer Interaction). The potential implications for our own species could also fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.RO (Robotics).
